{"tid":1860583,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"★[香港人!團結救自己!]-組織自己的口罩 分配Data Base","createTime":"2020-02-03T17:33:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T01:40:47.000Z","uid":133716,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"df2ed7913e6af0274fb9073c8320d61e782afea8","tid":1860583,"uid":133716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T17:33:18.000Z","msg":"口罩調撥/分派，個個鄰近地區都做做，但香港政府呢？<br />\n參考：一罩難求？各地政府怎樣做<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/130582\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F130582&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdMbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=c7c23a3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/130582</a><br />\n香港政府繼續與民為敵，沒有急市民所急，想市民所想。<br />\n全城都在瘋狂搶口罩、排幾個鐘隊、四圍打聽、個個網站去找。。。<br />\n這個政府有點兒太垃圾有點兒太無能，在口罩上仍在玩言語藝術：即將有XX個口罩到港，但即將是何時？又不派給市民！？<br />\n大家要自救！香港人！救自己！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>要設法分配，我們一班朋友唸過度過，其實都未必好難，現嘗試設立一個資料庫：香港人自己的口罩分配Data base</strong><br />\n<strong>目標：整理一做香港人的需口罩名單，會以計分方式按急緩調撥口罩，統一處理口罩的買賣/分發！希望人人有口罩！香港人！救自己！共同抗疫！</strong><br />\n以Database計分統籌分派方法好處：<br />\n&gt;避免囤積，有人有口罩，有人無口罩<br />\n&gt;可反映各人的需要口罩的逼切性，也盡可能能每人也能分配   <br />\n&gt;避免人流聚集<br />\n&gt;如有口罩的手足先放出口罩，日後有需要時優先取回購相關口罩數量<br />\n&gt;如果調撥得好，一個人夠分到一星期量已很好<br />\n<br />\n<strong>流程：</strong><br />\n1. 有意買口罩於google form填表計分，暫定表格及計分方法如下(一切以簡單為原則) <br />\n 買★[香港人!團結救自己!]-口罩 Data base (登記買口罩) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/hPKouwQSLiSSMVwAA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FhPKouwQSLiSSMVwAA&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdMbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=7910ca0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/hPKouwQSLiSSMVwAA</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZVY4guq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZVY4guq.jpg&h=d9791dec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3yP3w1S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3yP3w1S.jpg&h=c4ed6a9f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 有貨的賣家，可於google form填表<br />\n 賣☆[香港人!團結救自己!]-口罩 Data base (登記賣口罩) : <a href=\"https://forms.gle/4pMkeXL9DDLcZ4pf9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F4pMkeXL9DDLcZ4pf9&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdMbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=da0148d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/4pMkeXL9DDLcZ4pf9</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2stzDHu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2stzDHu.jpg&h=35520d46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3. 我們會將相關數量(分數較高者)的電郵地址及身份證頭3個數字交給賣家<br />\n4. 由賣家自行統一發電郵給有關人士，最重要是要交待貨時間及地點<br />\n5. 買家憑電郵及身份證買貨<br />\n<br />\n買★[香港人!團結救自己!]-口罩 Data base (登記買口罩) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/hPKouwQSLiSSMVwAA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FhPKouwQSLiSSMVwAA&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdMbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=7910ca0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/hPKouwQSLiSSMVwAA</a><br />\n賣☆[香港人!團結救自己!]-口罩 Data base (登記賣口罩) : <a href=\"https://forms.gle/4pMkeXL9DDLcZ4pf9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F4pMkeXL9DDLcZ4pf9&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdMbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=da0148d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/4pMkeXL9DDLcZ4pf9</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有關想法應該未必好完善，但正值打杖故先草草擬出來比大家<br />\n歡迎大家集思廣益及如真正實行也需要手足協助，歡迎大家TG我們：<a href=\"https://t.me/OurMarkDatabase\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FOurMarkDatabase&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdMbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=23e84e7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/OurMarkDatabase</a><br />\n<br />\n短期計劃：收集到一家數量的口罩買家暫定第1次會在收到1000個data base及有賣家時會開始分配買賣<br />\n<br />\n#我們團隊早前自己訂左20盒(唔多但都想出小小力)，共1000個口罩，到貨後會pack成10個一份，以郵寄/定點分賣給100個人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n#如果行得通，我們團隊嘗試將有關計分方法自動化<br />\n#如果招到足夠人手，我們可以代為分郵件通知、分小包、交收或寄出有關口罩<br />\n#香港人！救自己！"},{"pid":"f7424897046b60fb582adbf0cabc93268b77e2b3","tid":1860583,"uid":160214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T17:35:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"537c7ed66d428b8a6382404327dbfc3418d0588d","tid":1860583,"uid":133716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T17:37:15.000Z","msg":"簡短板：<br />\n香港人自己的口罩Data base<br />\n目標：整理一個香港人的需口罩名單，會以計分方式按急緩調撥口罩，統一處理口罩買賣/分發！希望人人有口罩！香港人！救自己！共同抗疫！<br />\n買★[香港人!團結救自己!]-口罩 Data base (登記買口罩) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/hPKouwQSLiSSMVwAA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FhPKouwQSLiSSMVwAA&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdMbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=7910ca0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/hPKouwQSLiSSMVwAA</a><br />\n賣☆[香港人!團結救自己!]-口罩 Data base (登記賣/分發口罩) : <a href=\"https://forms.gle/4pMkeXL9DDLcZ4pf9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F4pMkeXL9DDLcZ4pf9&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdMbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=da0148d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/4pMkeXL9DDLcZ4pf9</a><br />\n流程：<br />\n1. 有意買口罩，填表 <br />\n2. 有貨的賣家，填表<br />\n3. 我們會將相關數量(分數較高者)的電郵地址及身份證頭3個數字交給賣家<br />\n4. 由賣家自行統一發電郵給相關人士 <br />\n5. 買家憑電郵及身份證買貨<br />\n---------------------------------"},{"pid":"1919bb813cf2fee8de8fa43428316d930f89216d","tid":1860583,"uid":133716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T17:41:39.000Z","msg":"我地朋友用左成晚去傾，唔知可以走幾遠。但希望能出份力，救救自己"},{"pid":"0b11944200b58b4e97f4eb72c6a5ff64d2277e6c","tid":1860583,"uid":133716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T17:43:42.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"de52440f16a57afb161c5e86a0b0a479c78ded9a","tid":1860583,"uid":133716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T17:43:52.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"426e11548534b381cc66c071be95ab0376eb81c1","tid":1860583,"uid":133716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T17:44:03.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"ad5fdc733eb540f1193b126b170d3b642cdfa94e","tid":1860583,"uid":133716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s